<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Meri Website</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #667eea, #764ba2);
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 50px;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
    button {
      background: white;
      color: #764ba2;
      border: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    button:hover {
      background: #ddd;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>👋 Welcome to My Website!</h1>
  <p>Yeh meri pehli website hai jo GitHub Pages par chal rahi hai 🚀</p>
  <button onclick="alert('Thank you for visiting! ❤️')">Click Me</button>
</body>
</html>
